    <title lang="en">Dialog call</title>
    <para lang="en" >
      The dialog can be called in many ways :
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>      
          from the toolbox-menu:
          <guimenuitem><accel>F</accel>ile/<accel>D</accel>ialog/<accel>G</accel>radients</guimenuitem>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>      
          from the toolbox:
          clic on the current gradient
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          from the image-menu:
          <guimenuitem><accel>D</accel>ialog/<accel>G</accel>radients</guimenuitem>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          from an other dialog-menu:
          <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>dd Tab/<accel>G</accel>radients</guimenuitem>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </para>
  </simplesect> <!-- end Dialog call -->

